3.24.9 GetAtoms 
 

 
    
virtual OESystem::OEIterBase&lt;OEAtomBase&gt; *GetAtoms() const
    
Return an iterator over all the atoms of a molecule.  By default, this
returns all the atoms of the molecule in the order they were created.
The ordering of the atoms returned by GetAtoms may be modified by
OEMolBase::OrderAtoms.

  
    
virtual OESystem::OEIterBase&lt;OEAtomBase&gt; *GetAtoms(
  const OESystem::OEUnaryPredicate&lt;OEChem::OEAtomBase&gt; &amp;) const
    
Return an iterator over all of the atoms of a molecule that match the
specified atom predicate.

  

  
          
     
        
